Package: arimaPI
Title: Bayesian Prediction Intervals for ARIMA Processes
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2015-09-11
Author: Jouni Helske
Maintainer: Jouni Helske <jouni.helske@jyu.fi>
Imports: KFAS
Description: Bayesian prediction intervals for ARIMA processes with exogenous variables which take account the parameter uncertainty, leading to more accurate coverage probabilities in frequentist sense. Method uses importance sampling and root solving based on the predicted values and prediction errors.
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: yes
Encoding: UTF-8
